{"tid":1617444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［雙十中華民國國慶］賀賀佢","createTime":"2019-10-03T19:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:24:10.000Z","uid":9645,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6d3ac132b9cf70c8b39f4436ecd9c3ceb22bb8","tid":1617444,"uid":9645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見到行動Post 唔係太多人推<br />\n中共最唔想見到嘅<br />\n（繼英國 美國齊之後）<br />\n一定係青天白日滿地紅嘅中華民國旗🇹🇼<br />\n我地一定一定要好好賀一賀<br />\n 10/10 呢個國慶大日子<br />\n最好做到傳媒影出黎週街都係中華民國旗🇹🇼<br />\n比國際睇到我地舉邊度旗都好<br />\n死都唔會舉中共嘅國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4879eaf5f16065cae4414861cc008797885bf663","tid":1617444,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T19:49:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🇹🇼</span>"},{"pid":"65834e7369075f9f752682651b2ba2d37221c024","tid":1617444,"uid":9645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T20:06:22.000Z","msg":"隔離post 有人係咁話台灣朋友