wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗佢地見到外國人舉佢地支旗都會好感動，<br />\n之前有台灣10歲小朋友去參加比賽拎冠軍都披國旗<br />\n<br />\n<strong>【獨家】10歲童披國旗奪寶可夢世界冠軍 守諾分一半獎金給贈旗老闆</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190819/1619089/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190819%2F1619089%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c4a2b276\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190819%2F1619089%2F&h=3245d094\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190819/1619089/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從吳比上台到坐上決戰台，脖子上戴著他最愛的寶可夢烈空坐，幼小的身軀全程始終緊披著一面大國旗，網友們為之動容，留言表示：「太厲害了！這麼小就這麼愛國我都感動的流淚。」更封吳比為「台灣小智」，大讚這才是正港台灣之光。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f63b29d5c6e0037c3fcf1f1b09b2f4e5bb83d1df","tid":1617444,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500a0df64d353dcfb55d6c1116c6bfe122d6f037","tid":1617444,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0fe76a23916419b6f084949e0cc8f5dfcf263d","tid":1617444,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"🇹🇼"},{"pid":"7107e92bdf8e318905c2641ab6e7a1091e234e83","tid":1617444,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce59d85fd343b6fbc381a083a35b5e2765ac9d8","tid":1617444,"uid":101315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:07:38.000Z","msg":"對「更好的中國」有幻想的朋友 加油好嗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1641074/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1641074/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a6